FfeD-QLC MVP

Primary research attribution identifier:
https://orcid.org/0009-0007-2904-0443

QLC means Quasicrystal Lattice Cryptography in this repository.

This public MVP exposes only a bounded software scaffold:

- admissibility gate: accept, suspend, reject;
- Docker/CodeProject.AI study-case mapping;
- optional E2B sandbox smoke;
- Datadog-friendly labels and non-secret telemetry.

The repository intentionally does not disclose the full private research logic,
private keys, datasets, internal notebooks, or production cryptographic claims.

